<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Indro, fa velona
 Jesosy Tompon'aina !
 Foana ny fasana
 Resy izao Satana.
 Iza indray no hitomany,
 Raha nahare izany ?
 Ry foko sasatra
 Manahy fatratra,
 Heveronao izao ;
 Ho afaka ny sentonao !

[V2]
 Indro, fa velona
 Jesosy Tompon'aina !
 Izy nitsangana ;
 Ravo ny fo sy saina.
 Jeso Tompo nolatsaina
 Tonga loharanon'aina,
 Ry havana, andrandrao
 Ny lanitra izao :
 Jesosy velona,
 Ka azo ny fiainana !</lyrics>
<title>Indro fa velona FFPM132</title>
<author>C. Malan</author>
<hymn_number>132</hymn_number>
</song>